title: Hillary Clinton testifies — then and now
text: As the marathon testimony of Hillary Rodham Clinton before the House Select Committee on Benghazi got underway on Thursday morning, it was a strikingly different scene from her testimony almost three years ago on the same subject before the Senate Foreign Relations Committee.
